<h2><span style="float:left;">通假字</span></h2>
<a style="float:left; margin-top:7px; margin-left:5px;" href="javascript:PlayFanyi(68)"><img id="speakerimgFanyi68" src="/img/speaker.png" / alt="" width="16" height="16"/></a>
<span id="fanyiPlay68" style=" display:none;width:1px; height:1px; float:left;"></span>
