<a id="ding68" href="javascript:ding('68','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=c7a0f08d98cd')">有用(1140)</a><a id="pai68" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:pai('68','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=c7a0f08d98cd')">没用(194)</a>
